snippet.textDisplay: What an awesome track! have been listening to this on repeat... The lyrics are simple yet impactful... while everyone who is a part of this creation deserves resounding applause, I would like to highlight the simply superb performance by all the chorus singers and the percussion artist... The energy of the chorus singers adds a zing to the song... Watching them enjoy themselves while singing is a treat to the eyes! Can't tell you how delighted I am to witness this wonderful creation in my mother tongue Gujarati... This track's success should allow us to bring our folk songs to such an international platform... Zaverchand Meghani's Charan Kanya, Shivaji nu halardu could be a good starting point... We have outstanding musical talent from Gujarat - singers, composers, lyricists...  May this flow continue... Vaheva do vaheva do...
